  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list>
<item>Classify magnetic materials as paramagnetic, diamagnetic, or ferromagnetic, based on their response to a magnetic field</item>
<item>Sketch how magnetic dipoles align with the magnetic field in each type of substance</item>
<item>Define hysteresis and magnetic susceptibility, which determines the type of magnetic material</item>
</list></md:abstract>
