<exercise id="fs-id1166168227099">
<problem id="fs-id1166168227101">
<para id="fs-id1166168227103">The accompanying figure shows a long, straight wire carrying a current of 10 A. What is the magnetic force on an electron at the instant it is 20 cm from the wire, traveling parallel to the wire with a speed of <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2.0</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:msup><m:mtext>m/s?</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math> Describe qualitatively the subsequent motion of the electron.</para>
